01:43:57,980 --> 01:44:03,420
What is it? Diver farts. Those bastards are dumping complex organics into the atmosphere.

1139
01:44:04,300 --> 01:44:11,180
How complex. Hard to tell so far. Faint traces and they dissipate like that. But sugars and

1140
01:44:11,180 --> 01:44:20,060
aminos at least. Maybe proteins. Maybe more. Maybe life. Microbes. An alien terraforming project.

