03:47:15,420 --> 03:47:18,700
I've discussed it with the rest of the gang, Isaac. We're all agreed.

2620
03:47:19,740 --> 03:47:24,140
All agreed? You don't have a working majority in there, Suze. Just because you cut your brain

2621
