07:01:18,620 --> 07:01:22,540
the one that lets you go home to your family after work and play with your children and sleep at

4637
07:01:22,540 --> 07:01:29,580
night. Never humanize your victims. It shouldn't have been such an issue when dealing with methane

4638
07:01:29,580 --> 07:01:36,700
breathing Medusae. I guess every little bit helped. Bio-telemetry danced across the headspace beside

4639
