each alien, luminous annotation shuddering through thin air. I had no idea what constituted normal

4640
07:01:42,620 --> 07:01:48,300
relings for these creatures, but I couldn't imagine these jagged spikes passing for anything but bad

4641
07:01:48,300 --> 07:01:54,620
news. The creatures themselves seethed subtly with fine mosaics in blue and gray, fluid patterns

4642
07:01:54,620 --> 07:02:00,300
