4663
07:04:13,740 --> 07:04:20,940
Clench had pressed the tip of one arm against the touchpad. The icon there glowed like a candle flame.

4664
07:04:23,100 --> 07:04:27,580
Six and a half minutes later, they'd graduated from yellow squares to time-lapse four-dimensional

4665
