4735
07:11:23,100 --> 07:11:27,020
Out here in the endless wastelands of the oar, there was no room for a live and let live.

4736
07:11:27,660 --> 07:11:33,340
Never mind what the other has done or what it hasn't. Think of what it could do, if it were

4737
