5408
08:18:05,260 --> 08:18:08,700
It hurt just to breathe. I was so alone.

5409
08:18:10,460 --> 08:18:15,020
Webbing pressed against the curve of my back, bounced me forward gently as a breeze, caught

5410
08:18:15,020 --> 08:18:21,580
