08:32:22,380 --> 08:32:24,620
The load bearing beams just couldn't take the strain.

5556
08:32:25,500 --> 08:32:27,820
All of them I began to realize had missed the point.

5557
08:32:28,700 --> 08:32:33,420
All those theories, all those drug dreams and experiments and models trying to prove what

5558
08:32:33,420 --> 08:32:39,020
