5559
08:32:39,100 --> 08:32:44,380
Consciousness makes us what we are. It lets us see the beauty and the ugliness.

5560
08:32:44,380 --> 08:32:47,180
It elevates us into the exalted realm of the spiritual.

5561
08:32:47,900 --> 08:32:53,500
Oh, a few outsiders, Dawkins, Coe, the occasional writer of hack work fiction who barely achieved

5562
